# ============================================
# 白名单模式：忽略一切，只追踪关键文件
# ============================================

# 忽略所有文件（但 * 不影响目录遍历）
*

# 允许所有目录被遍历（关键！）
!*/

# ============================================
# 核心配置文件
# ============================================
!AGENTS.md
!SOUL.md
!PROFILE.md
!MEMORY.md
!.gitignore
!README.md

# agent.json 包含个人路径和密钥，已排除
agent.json

# ============================================
# 记忆系统（学生数据模板）
# ============================================
!memory/student/profile.md
!memory/student/knowledge_matrix.md
!memory/student/templates.md
!memory/student/error_log.md
!memory/student/contest_log.md
!memory/student/conversation_log.md
!memory/student/INDEX.md

# ============================================
# 所有 Skills 的 SKILL.md
# ============================================
!skills/*/SKILL.md

# ============================================
# Skills 依赖的文件
# ============================================
!skills/browser_cdp/SKILL.md
!skills/browser_visible/SKILL.md
!skills/channel_message/SKILL.md
!skills/copaw_source_index/SKILL.md
!skills/cron/SKILL.md
!skills/dingtalk_channel/SKILL.md

!skills/docx/SKILL.md
!skills/docx/LICENSE.txt
!skills/docx/scripts/*.py
!skills/docx/scripts/**/*.py
!skills/docx/scripts/templates/*.xml
!skills/docx/scripts/office/schemas/**/*.xsd

!skills/file_reader/SKILL.md
!skills/guidance/SKILL.md
!skills/himalaya/SKILL.md
!skills/himalaya/references/*.md
!skills/multi_agent_collaboration/SKILL.md
!skills/news/SKILL.md

!skills/pdf/SKILL.md
!skills/pdf/LICENSE.txt
!skills/pdf/reference.md
!skills/pdf/forms.md
!skills/pdf/scripts/*.py

!skills/pptx/SKILL.md
!skills/pptx/LICENSE.txt
!skills/pptx/editing.md
!skills/pptx/pptxgenjs.md
!skills/pptx/scripts/*.py
!skills/pptx/scripts/**/*.py
!skills/pptx/scripts/office/schemas/**/*.xsd

!skills/xlsx/SKILL.md
!skills/xlsx/LICENSE.txt
!skills/xlsx/scripts/*.py
!skills/xlsx/scripts/**/*.py
!skills/xlsx/scripts/office/schemas/**/*.xsd

!skills/urlgo/SKILL.md
!skills/urlgo/steps/*.md

# ============================================
# 竞赛教练专属 Skills - 完整内容
# ============================================

# 题单与训练计划生成器
!skills/problem_set_generator/SKILL.md
!skills/problem_set_generator/knowledge_map.md
!skills/problem_set_generator/templates/*.md

# 搬题姬
!skills/搬题姬/SKILL.md
!skills/搬题姬/*.md
!skills/搬题姬/question/*.cpp
!skills/搬题姬/question/*.h
!skills/搬题姬/question/*.yaml
!skills/搬题姬/question/testdata/*.yaml

# 备课
!skills/备课/SKILL.md
!skills/备课/references/*.md
!skills/备课/assets/*.md

# 命题工坊
!skills/命题工坊/SKILL.md

# 墨池
!skills/墨池/SKILL.md
!skills/墨池/inkpot.py
!skills/墨池/record.py
!skills/墨池/TEST_REPORT.md
!skills/墨池/knowledge/**/*.md
!skills/墨池/profile/*.md
# 墨池的 db/ 是用户个人数据，不追踪

# 学生刷题日报
!skills/学生刷题日报/SKILL.md
!skills/学生刷题日报/*.py

# 智国学堂
!skills/智国学堂/SKILL.md
!skills/智国学堂/*.md

# ============================================
# Python 缓存忽略
# ============================================
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc

# ============================================
# 运行数据（不追踪）
# ============================================
browser/
file_store/
tool_result/
sessions/
node_modules/
.eme_store*
.reme_store*
.bootstrap_completed
HEARTBEAT.md
jobs.json
chats.json
memory_file_metadata.json
skill.json
.skill.json.lock
